  "title": "Y Is There AutoJump",
  "description": "Stop the annoying autojump is on by default feature.",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/670/174/bh_aj_header.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1142\" height=\"329\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/670/171/bh_aj_banner1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1142\" height=\"173\" /></p>\n<p>I ported this from Al132's No Default Auto-Jump which is MIT licensed and can be found at&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/no-default-auto-jump\">https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/no-default-auto-jump</a>&nbsp;it was really easy to port forward to 1.16.1. Al is a coding GOD.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/670/172/bh_aj_banner2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1142\" height=\"173\" />&nbsp;</p>\n<p>What it does is on first run of a client where the mod exists, it turns off the autojump feature. The player can turn it back on later if they like.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/670/173/bh_aj_banner3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1142\" height=\"173\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/ngNQjT5\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://discordapp.com/api/guilds/96753964485181440/widget.png?style=banner2\" /></a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/kreezxil\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://s12.directupload.net/images/200916/joj33k55.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/MinecraftModdedForge\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://s12.directupload.net/images/200916/efhmdjhg.png\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://kreezcraft.com/y-is-there-autojump\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/670/175/bh_aj_promo.png\" alt=\"Bisect Hosting\" width=\"90%\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">If you want a server setup using Y is there Autojump with zero effort, get a <a href=\"https://kreezcraft.com/y-is-there-autojump\">server with BisectHosting</a> and receive 25% off your first month as a new customer using the code kreezxil</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
